data.description: Welcome home to Piedmont Crescent, a historic gem in the heart of Midtown Atlanta. This unit has been beautifully updated to create a more modern design and open floorplan while still maintaining its period charm. Natural light floods the space, highlighting the tall ceilings and recently replaced hardwood floors. The brand new, fully renovated kitchen is completely customized with a hidden panel refrigerator/freezer and dishwasher, induction cooktop, and thoughtful storage solutions throughout. The best part? If you don’t like the white or the handles, you can easily replace with something else or switch up the inserts to create your own custom kitchen. The bathroom was also recently updated and the bedroom is large enough for a king sized bed. Extend your living space and enjoy your morning coffee or an evening cocktail on your charming patio off the living room with views of the impeccably maintained courtyard. The furnace is just 3 years old and the unit includes one dedicated parking space as well as a shared storage unit. Conveniently located just steps from Piedmont Park, you'll have easy access to outdoor recreation, Marta, and all the vibrant dining, shopping, and entertainment options that Midtown has to offer!
